=========================
Product Analytic Donation
=========================

This module is a glue module between the *product_analytic* and
*donation* modules.

Usage
=====

When you create a donation line with a product that has an
**income analytic account** (or whose internal category has an
**income analytic account**), it will be automatically set on the
donation line.
